title: 163: The Aldi Haul Episode (February '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Aldi Haul Episode (February '22 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Jamie & Mikey are taste-testing 14 finds from ALDI! Yummy stuff like egg wraps, many different types of cheeses, coconut cashews, a teriyaki sriracha bowl, popped corn crisps, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus a grilled-cheese-inspired find that received a 10 out of 10 on Lisa’s rating scale that you need to buy right away! The wait is over... PUSH PLAY NOW, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: It’s our first Aldi "Hauldi" of the year and boy, was it one of the best ever!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
